title.rendered: Orthocare Dosicare Maternity Pelvis & Lumbar Region Pregnancy Support Strap Belt – Medium

content.rendered:
Low lumbar and SIJ pregnancy support.
Indication
Low back and SIJ pain in pregnancy, acute back pain, degenerative spinal changes, paravertebral spasm, illiosacral irritations.
Mode of Action
Provides support and stability from pelvis to lumbar region.
Features
  • Skin friendly material.
  • High quality elastic fabric.
  • Easy to fit and remove due to practical velcro system.
  • Extra stability and support from adjustable straps.
  • Soft springs for comfort.

For sizing measure around waist as below:

Small: 70-85cm

Medium: 85-100cm

Large: 100-115cm
